description: Ahoy, matey! If you’re seeking gold in the form of a cold dessert, shiver me timbers! X marks the spot. Treasure Ice Land is the ultimate jackpot!With a top of the line shaver shavin' up nicely fine ice, a self-serve station that offers all your flavor faves, and a delectable selection of premium ice creams (Ben & Jerry's, Haagen Dazs, Magnum, etc..), you’ll just have to get your booty over to Treasure Ice Land for a pleasurable sweet retreat from the desert heat.
name: Treasure Ice Land
